    "Background": {
      "text": "Multiple types of oral and intravenous therapy available\nIV therapy is usually reserved for patients undergoing epoetin therapy or severely anemic\nJehovah's Witness patients\nShould be cautiously administered due to the risk of\nanaphylaxis\nwith some preparations.\n[1]",
